comments:
They all had the same shape at the end.

Associating the second and third shape to a specific image.

The hard part was at the end, when trying to guess after seeing the image disappear so quickly. The easier part was in the beginning when getting to associate the shapes to the images.

I think the repetition that occurred in the beginning was key to making the association a lot easier. In future maybe slow down the disappearance of the image a little.
